434382,104,333,2,5,1,15,3,Yaṃ pana vuttaṃ–
434383,104,333,6,34,1,105,17,"‘‘ apasādento’’ ti, tattha ayaṃ adhippāyo– ānanda,‘‘ atha ca pana me uttānakuttānako viya khāyatī’’ ti mā hevaṃ avaca. "
434384,104,333,35,55,1,142,18,"Yadi hi te esa uttānakuttānako viya khāyati, kasmā tvaṃ attano dhammatāya sotāpanno nāhosi, mayā dinnanayeva ṭhatvā sotāpattimaggaṃ paṭivijjhasi. "
434385,104,333,56,84,1,234,24,"Ānanda, idaṃ nibbānameva gambhīraṃ, paccayākāro pana tava uttānako jāto, atha kasmā oḷārikaṃ kāmarāgasaṃyojanaṃ paṭighasaṃyojanaṃ, oḷārikaṃ kāmarāgānusayaṃ paṭighānusayanti ime cattāro kilese samugghāṭetvā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ na sacchikarosi? "
