439472,104,1306,2,19,1,117,10,"360. Arūpakammaṭṭhāne yaṃ tassa pākaṭaṃ vedanāvasena abhinivesamukhaṃ, tameva dassetuṃ somanassaṃpāhaṃ, {devānamindā}tiādimāha. "
